item.title: CVE-2018-20252|2024-09-16T18:24:07.685Z -- check%20point%20software%20technologies%20ltd. -- winrar
item.description: In WinRAR versions prior to and including 5.60, there is an out-of-bounds write vulnerability during parsing of crafted ACE and RAR archive formats. Successful exploitation could lead to arbitrary code execution in the context of the current user.
